{"id":576939,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/【立此存照】来自日语的现代医学用语及名词一览/","date":"2018-01-20T10:06:05Z","modified":"2018-01-20T10:06:05Z","title":"【立此存照】来自日语的现代医学用语及名词一览","content":"<blockquote style=\"width: 68%;\"><p><strong>相关阅读： </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e5%a4%a7%e8%b1%a1%e5%85%ac%e4%bc%9a-%e5%86%b3%e4%b8%8d%e5%85%81%e8%ae%b8%e6%97%a5%e8%af%ad%e7%8e%b7%e6%b1%a1%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%87/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">大象公会 | 决不允许日语玷污中文</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/10/%e5%bf%83%e4%b9%8b%e6%b0%b8%e6%81%92%ef%bc%9a%e8%ae%ba%e6%89%93call%e4%b8%80%e8%af%8d%e7%81%ab%e9%81%8d%e5%85%a8%e7%bd%91%e5%85%b6%e4%b8%ad%e7%9a%84%e6%bb%a5%e7%94%a8%e5%8f%8a/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">心之永恒：论“打call”一词火遍全网其中的滥用及负面因素</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1878363622/FFeaMruLS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@勿怪幸</a>：要废除“患者”一词的20位，如果是别的行业还勉强可以理解。偏偏是医学界的。医学用语80%是日语。不用日语，医学就没法进行。看看这些医学日语的词。还真难找出一个现代医学中文中不是来自日语的。 ​​​​</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0h0ch46j20ku0ynn16.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576942\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0h0ch46j20ku0ynn16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"831\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0h0ch46j20ku0ynn16.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0h0ch46j20ku0ynn16-180x300.jpg 180w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0h0ch46j20ku0ynn16-616x1024.jpg 616w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0hdf4a6j20ku0z50y6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576943\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0hdf4a6j20ku0z50y6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"843\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0hdf4a6j20ku0z50y6.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0hdf4a6j20ku0z50y6-178x300.jpg 178w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0hdf4a6j20ku0z50y6-607x1024.jpg 607w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0goidcdj20ku0zadj8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576941\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0goidcdj20ku0zadj8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"846\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0goidcdj20ku0zadj8.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0goidcdj20ku0zadj8-177x300.jpg 177w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/6ff58de6gy1fnn0goidcdj20ku0zadj8-605x1024.jpg 605w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/3951975029/FFeDBCCVn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@日本小小智</a>：</p>\n<p>图一，这20位爱国专家，希望废除源自日语的汉字“患者”，改成“病人”，以彰显爱国之情。</p>\n<p>不管是揣摩上意，做些漂亮的事情给上面看，还是真的爱国之心促使，都觉得相当幼稚。</p>\n<p>图二，东京外科博士<a href=\"https://weibo.com/n/%E5%8B%BF%E6%80%AA%E5%B9%B8?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@勿怪幸</a> 整理的来自日本的医学汉字，目前中国的医学用语80%来自日语，是打算全部废除？</p>\n<p>图三，现代汉语词汇来自日本汉字一览，如果要废除，可以请彻底一点吗？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/eb8e5a75gy1fnn2gc7sx1j20j7340b29.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576944\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/eb8e5a75gy1fnn2gc7sx1j20j7340b29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"2626\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/eb8e5a75gy1fnn2l092ezj20ri3kk7p5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576954\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/01/eb8e5a75gy1fnn2l092ezj20ri3kk7p5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"2338\" srcset=